This repository uses the Agentile methodology. Before writing ANY code:

1. Read .agentile/AGENT_ENTRY.md (decision tree for all contributors)
2. Read .agentile/CONFIG.md (canonical project constants)
3. Read .agentile/rules/CORE_RULES.md (non-negotiable rules)
4. Check .agentile/sprints/CURRENT.md (active sprint)

GATE: Do NOT write code until you have read these files.

Rules: No mocks/stubs/TODOs. Test count only goes up. Linting clean. Every feature traces to a sprint item.

Full framework: .agentile/docs/AGENTILE_METHODOLOGY.md
